textBeforeTable: 2010 NCCAA DIVISION 1 MEN'S SOCCER (Region Chair poll) The Panthers received 22 points in the latest poll which included games as of Sept. 14.  At the time, Greenville held a record of 2-2. GREENVILLE, Ill. -- For the third straight week, the Greenville men's soccer team has received a ranking in the NCCAA Division I men's soccer coaches' poll.  This week Greenville is No. 8 in the nation.
